title: Distinctive lower case L
content:

The majority of the letters appear to be Delphin, with the |K| and |y| from some other typeface substituted:  
 [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/delphin/](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317155213/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/delphin/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/delphin/")
